      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DISTORTED HUMOUR (2) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split and ran away with a one length win at Healesville over 300m in 16.84. The form out of his last race has been franked. One of the key runners again. BRAEMAR MOLLY (3) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (17.45) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at Healesville. Can turn it around this time. FEROCIOUS CANARY (4) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Geelong over 400m behind Summer Spritz (23.56) in a Grade 5. One of the main contenders. REDEEMER BELLE (1) is new to this course but can play a major role.",
